<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 19.5px; font-weight: bold;">For more information or to book our Twin Centre Holidays &amp; Tours please call 01483 79 11 11</p>
<p>Discover Slovenia by combining the contrasting resorts we feature. Combine the cultural city of <a data-udi="umb://document/5cfd5f91c1d0419185792bc414ff7721" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5cfd5f91c1d0419185792bc414ff7721}" title="Ljubljana">Ljubljana</a> and enjoy the restaurants and great nightlife with a relaxing stay in the beautiful resort of <a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled">Lake Bled</a> and visit the only island in <a data-udi="umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049}" title="Slovenia">Slovenia</a>. Or head to the mountains and the wonderful resorts of <a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab}" title="Kranjska Gora">Kranjska Gora</a> and Lake Bohinj. Kranjska Gora has stunning views towards the Julian Alps and the distant peaks of the Karavanke mountains. <a data-udi="umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753}" title="Lake Bohinj">Lake Bohinj</a> is famous for its crystal clear waters and is the source of the mighty River Soca. </p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Multi Centre Combinations</h2>
<ul>
<li>All resorts can be combined for 3, 4 or 7 night stays. Choose hotels that suit you.</li>
<li>All transfers will be direct between resorts except from Ljubljana which will operate via the airport. Transfers are on Wednesdays and Saturdays only.</li>
<li>You can create a 2, 3 or 4 centre holiday. For example, 4 nights + 3 nights + 4 nights + 3 nights = 14 night 4 centre holiday</li>
<li>Prices include flights, accommodation with meals as specified and all transfers.</li>
</ul>
<p>Shown below are some of the most popular combinations, but other resorts and hotel combinations are possible.</p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Julian Alps Jewels (3 centre holiday)</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13054377/julian-alps.jpg" alt="Julian Alps Jewels (3 centre holiday)" rel="878,150" /></p>
<p><br /><strong>11 nights: 4 nights Bled, 3 nights Bohinj and 4 nights Kranjska Gora</strong></p>
<p><strong>Standard accommodation:</strong> <strong>Bled</strong> (<a data-udi="umb://document/dcb6eed2838a4451bda1ddff9ee5e9f6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dcb6eed2838a4451bda1ddff9ee5e9f6}" title="Hotel Jelovica">Bledrose Hotel</a>) - <strong>Bohinj</strong> (<a data-udi="umb://document/2aeb8216bf2947b9951b9a65f072cf51" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2aeb8216bf2947b9951b9a65f072cf51}" title="Hotel Jezero">Hotel Jezero</a>) - <strong>Kranjska Gora</strong> (<a data-udi="umb://document/7705f5943aac4ce4921c9a6b9fd70642" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7705f5943aac4ce4921c9a6b9fd70642}" title="Best Western Hotel Kranjska Gora (formerly Hotel Lek)">Hotel Lek</a>). Price from <strong>£1,171</strong> per person including flights, accommodation on half board and all transfers.</p>
<p><strong>Superior accommodation:</strong> <strong>Bled</strong> (<a data-udi="umb://document/7da02416d69d4cefb0f91e9512835dc5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7da02416d69d4cefb0f91e9512835dc5}" title="Hotel Astoria">Hotel Astoria</a>) - <strong>Bohinj</strong> (<a data-udi="umb://document/e06cfb2dd33f494e88ac01de07d9193e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e06cfb2dd33f494e88ac01de07d9193e}" title="Hotel Kristal">Hotel Kristal</a>) - <strong>Kranjska Gora</strong> (<a data-udi="umb://document/7705f5943aac4ce4921c9a6b9fd70642" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7705f5943aac4ce4921c9a6b9fd70642}" title="Best Western Hotel Kranjska Gora (formerly Hotel Lek)">Hotel Lek</a>). Price from <strong>£1,270</strong> per person including flights, accommodation on half board and all transfers.</p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div>Other combinations are possible. Please call our reservations team on 01483 79 11 11 to book these holidays</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><strong>General Terms and Conditions:</strong> All prices, offers and availability are correct at time of publishing, are subject to change &amp; availability and can be withdrawn at any time. All offers are for 7 nights unless otherwise stated. All prices are per person based on maximum occupancy of a room or apartment and on the lowest priced departure point, supplements for other flights/airports may apply. </p>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
